  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Manifest arsenic skin lesions (melanosis, leucomelanosis, or keratosis)

          -  Aged 25 to 65 years

          -  Permanent resident of study area

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Clinically too ill (enlarged spleen or liver)

          -  Presence of gangrene

          -  Cancer
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
